pidgin-libnotify: Pidgin Notification Daemon Plugin
pidgin-libnotify:
pidgin-libnotify: This plugin adds a libnotify interface to pidgin, enabling popups
pidgin-libnotify: much like guifications. It has some configuration options, to show
pidgin-libnotify: popups when a buddy signs on, on new messages and on new
pidgin-libnotify: conversations only.
pidgin-libnotify:
pidgin-libnotify: URL: http://gaim-libnotify.sourceforge.net/
